summary: I graduated from the master in Chemistry at the Radboud University Nijmegen. During my studies, I became acquainted with interesting challenges in organic chemistry. Currently, Iâ€™m focusing on the chemistry of carbohydrates and I want to become a better researcher in this field. During my studies I worked on a variety of project at the Fontys University of Applied Science Eindhoven (Netherlands), Bangor University Wales (UK), Radboud University Nijmegen (Netherlands), and Massachusetts Institute of Technology (USA). I am looking forward to working on interesting projects in the field of organic chemistry.
